{"type":"message","id":"f5666cf0","parentId":"e4b43c2c","timestamp":"2026-04-25T09:30:12.177Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. If runtime-provided startup context is included for this first turn, use it before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Saturday, April 25th, 2026 - 5:29 PM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-25 09:29 UTC"}],"timestamp":1777109412091}}
