{"type":"message","id":"f258483a","parentId":"f369247d","timestamp":"2026-04-25T09:30:39.326Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_lcU5ioE4NQhBfrUJcIcdGl6O|fc_03de1a6cc6aa873f0169ec89be63a48196ba7ec32d5b5131a3","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: gpt-image-generator\ndescription: Generate and edit images using a custom GPT responses API. Use when the user requests GPT-based image generation (text-to-image) or image editing (image-to-image).\n---\n\n# GPT Image Generator\n\nThis skill provides Python scripts to generate and edit images via a custom API endpoint.\n\n## Setup\n\nBefore using this skill, the user must configure the API URL and Key. An example configuration is provided in `references/env.example`.\n\nUsers should set these environment variables:\n- `PY_IMAGE_GEN_API_URL`\n- `PY_IMAGE_GEN_API_KEY`\n\n## Workflow\n\n### Text to Image\n\nGenerate an image from a prompt:\n\n```bash\npython3 skills/gpt-image-generator/scripts/generate_image.py \"your prompt here\"\n```\n\n### Image to Image (Edit)\n\nEdit an existing image based on a prompt:\n\n```bash\npython3 skills/gpt-image-generator/scripts/generate_image_edit.py --image <path-to-image> --prompt \"edit instructions\"\n```\n\n## Important Notes\n\n- The scripts save the generated image in the current working directory.\n- Always use the `message` tool to send the generated image back to the user immediately after success.\n- If editing, always pass the absolute path of the user's latest provided image to `--image`.\n- You can pass `--out-base <name>` to customize the output file prefix.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777109439259}}
{"type":"message","id":"e222b2ca","parentId":"f258483a","timestamp":"2026-04-25T09:30:44.689Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"可以，直接把你要生成的画面描述发我。  \n我会按 **gpt-image-2** 来出图，如果你愿意，一次最好顺手带上这几个信息：**主体、风格、画幅比例（1:1 / 3:4 / 16:9）、是否要带字**。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_03de1a6cc6aa873f0169ec89c313e0819694f13944b83e4018\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":35620,"output":77,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35697,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777109439328,"responseId":"resp_03de1a6cc6aa873f0169ec89c07be481969be0f6e916ca4f66"}}
