{"type":"message","id":"c256cb4e","parentId":"65634130","timestamp":"2026-04-25T09:41:38.355Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"测出来了，这次不是 key 问题。  \n现在服务端明确返回：\n\n`model gpt-image-2 is only supported on /v1/images/generations and /v1/images/edits`\n\n结论很清楚：\n- 你这个 `china.unicom-online.cloud:8317` 代理 **不支持在 `/v1/responses` 上跑 `gpt-image-2`**\n- 它只接受：\n  - `/v1/images/generations`\n  - `/v1/images/edits`\n\n也就是说，**当前不是 .env 配错了，而是 gpt-image-generator 这份脚本走错了接口类型**。\n\n下一步最合理有 2 条：\n\n1. **我直接改脚本**\n   让 `gpt-image-generator` 在 `gpt-image-2` 时自动走 `/v1/images/generations`\n   这是最彻底的修法，我建议这个\n\n2. **临时换服务端**\n   找一个支持 `/v1/responses + image_generation` 的代理，不改脚本直接继续用\n\n如果你点头，我就直接走 **方案 1**，把脚本改成真正适配你这条代理。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_03de1a6cc6aa873f0169ec8c4d42b88196a95a5f849446b8a4\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":48984,"output":264,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49248,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777110090390,"responseId":"resp_03de1a6cc6aa873f0169ec8c4bbbb88196bc56ed4fc3eeaa72"}}
