{"type":"message","id":"eee85636","parentId":"983fc6e1","timestamp":"2026-04-25T09:47:55.475Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"openclaw-weixin:1777110471723-36c6467a\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-04-25 17:47 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\n{\n \"photo_type\": \"结婚登记照\",\n \"specifications\": {\n \"size\": \"两寸证件照\",\n \"aspect_ratio\": \"3:2\",\n \"requirement\": \"保持原图五官\"\n },\n \"background\": {\n \"color\": \"深红色\",\n \"hex\": \"#8B0000\",\n \"type\": \"纯色背景\",\n \"description\": \"经典结婚登记照红色背景，无渐变，色彩饱满均匀\"\n },\n \"composition\": {\n \"orientation\": \"女左男右\",\n \"positioning\": \"女性在前，男性略侧后，但是两方外侧肩膀基本齐平，女性则两侧肩膀齐平\",\n \"framing\": \"半身照\",\n \"crop\": \"从胸部上方到头顶，保留适当头顶空间\",\n \"distance\": \"男性肩膀在女性肩膀后侧，略贴紧，女性正脸朝前，男性头部稍微朝中间\",\n \"angle\": \"平视正面拍摄\",\n \"lighting\": \"正面柔和打光，无明显阴影，光线均匀\"\n },\n \"female\": {\n \"hairstyle\": {\n \"type\": \"长发过胸，轻度蓬松\",\n \"color\": \"黑色\",\n \"details\": \"头发整洁，露出额头、眉毛和双耳，一侧长发在前\",\n \"style\": \"优雅端庄，适合证件照\"\n },\n \"expression\": {\n \"type\": \"露齿微笑\",\n \"smile\": \"自然微笑，露出8颗牙齿\",\n \"eyes\": \"眼神温和亲切，微微带笑\",\n \"overall\": \"自信幸福，温柔大方\"\n },\n \"clothing\": {\n \"type\": \"法式轻奢礼服裙\",\n \"color\": \"纯白色\",\n \"style\": \"柔滑锻面轻裹肩颈，流畅褶皱自然垂落，勾勒温婉线条\",\n \"sleeves\": \"无袖\",\n \"fabric\": \"缎面\",\n \"description\": \"\"\n },\n \"makeup\": {\n \"base\": \"清透底妆，肤色均匀\",\n \"eyebrows\": \"自然眉形，颜色与发色相近\",\n \"eyes\": \"淡雅眼妆，细眼线，睫毛自然\",\n \"lips\": \"红色/珊瑚色口红，饱满有光泽\",\n \"blush\": \"自然腮红，提升气色\"\n },\n \"accessories\": {\n \"earrings\": \"珍珠吊坠耳环，简约优雅\",\n \"other\": \"无其他明显配饰\"\n },\n \"pose\": {\n \"orientation\": \"正面朝向镜头\",\n \"shoulders\": \"肩部微微侧向男性\",\n \"posture\": \"挺直背部，优雅端庄\"\n }\n },\n \"male\": {\n \"hairstyle\": {\n \"type\": \"侧分短发\",\n \"color\": \"黑色\",\n \"details\": \"头发整齐梳理，侧分造型，长度适中\",\n \"style\": \"干练利落，商务正式\"\n },\n \"expression\": {\n \"type\": \"露齿微笑\",\n \"smile\": \"自然微笑，露出牙齿\",\n \"eyes\": \"眼神温和自信\",\n \"overall\": \"儒雅稳重，亲切友善\"\n },\n \"clothing\": {\n \"suit\": {\n \"color\": \"蓝黑色\",\n \"type\": \"双排扣西装\",\n \"style\": \"2026现代正式商务款\"\n },\n \"shirt\": {\n \"color\": \"纯白色\",\n \"collar\": \"标准领\"\n },\n \"tie\": {\n \"color\": \"蓝黑色\",\n \"pattern\": \"金色/浅色小圆点图案\",\n \"knot\": \"标准领带结\"\n }\n },\n \"makeup\": {\n \"base\": \"自然肤色\",\n \"facial_hair\": \"无胡茬\"\n },\n \"pose\": {\n \"orientation\": \"男性头部稍微朝中间，显得有层次感\",\n \"shoulders\": \"端正挺拔\",\n \"posture\": \"站姿挺拔，精神饱满\"\n }\n },\n \"overall_style\": {\n \"tone\": \"正式、优雅、温馨\",\n \"atmosphere\": \"庄重而不失亲切，经典结婚登记照风格\",\n \"color_palette\": [\n \"深红色\",\n \"纯白色\",\n \"深蓝色\"\n ],\n \"mood\": \"幸福、和谐、庄重\"\n }\n}"}],"timestamp":1777110475402}}
{"type":"message","id":"6a8eced5","parentId":"eee85636","timestamp":"2026-04-25T09:48:00.729Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ulpfwEA0cFJg02rDqgt4gcwM|fc_03de1a6cc6aa873f0169ec8dcfda0c81969a686f874775f176","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/skills/gpt-image-generator/SKILL.md","offset":1,"limit":120},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"~/.openclaw/skills/gpt-image-generator/SKILL.md\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":120}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":53748,"output":39,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53787,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777110475475,"responseId":"resp_03de1a6cc6aa873f0169ec8dce31108196890aba3a77809fce"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ff9aaae5","parentId":"6a8eced5","timestamp":"2026-04-25T09:48:00.870Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ulpfwEA0cFJg02rDqgt4gcwM|fc_03de1a6cc6aa873f0169ec8dcfda0c81969a686f874775f176","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: gpt-image-generator\ndescription: Generate and edit images using a custom GPT responses API. Use when the user requests GPT-based image generation (text-to-image) or image editing (image-to-image).\n---\n\n# GPT Image Generator\n\nThis skill provides Python scripts to generate and edit images via a custom API endpoint.\n\n## Setup\n\nBefore using this skill, the user must configure the API URL and Key. An example configuration is provided in `references/env.example`.\n\nUsers should set these environment variables:\n- `PY_IMAGE_GEN_API_URL`\n- `PY_IMAGE_GEN_API_KEY`\n\n## Workflow\n\n### Text to Image\n\nGenerate an image from a prompt:\n\n```bash\npython3 skills/gpt-image-generator/scripts/generate_image.py \"your prompt here\"\n```\n\n### Image to Image (Edit)\n\nEdit an existing image based on a prompt:\n\n```bash\npython3 skills/gpt-image-generator/scripts/generate_image_edit.py --image <path-to-image> --prompt \"edit instructions\"\n```\n\n## Important Notes\n\n- The scripts save the generated image in the current working directory.\n- Always use the `message` tool to send the generated image back to the user immediately after success.\n- If editing, always pass the absolute path of the user's latest provided image to `--image`.\n- You can pass `--out-base <name>` to customize the output file prefix.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777110480803}}
{"type":"message","id":"50ecbc1b","parentId":"ff9aaae5","timestamp":"2026-04-25T09:48:15.682Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我直接按这份规格出图，但先提醒一句：你这段里写了“保持原图五官”，**目前你还没发原图**，所以我现在只能先按你给的文字规格生成风格接近版，不能保证五官一致。","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_03de1a6cc6aa873f0169ec8dd43f1c8196888444ecb63ab22c\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_xojcfztkEXtNXlPwPd77WmK0|fc_03de1a6cc6aa873f0169ec8dd593a88196849120bf046a9011","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 ~/.openclaw/skills/gpt-image-generator/scripts/generate_image.py --api-url http://china.unicom-online.cloud:8317/v1/responses --api-key sk-K4yKam5TDcrCSs67S --model gpt-image-2 --out-base /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/generated-images/marriage-photo-red-bg-3x2 \"结婚登记照，双人半身证件照，两寸比例 3:2，正式、优雅、温馨、庄重而亲切。纯色深红色背景，经典结婚登记照红底，无渐变，色彩饱满均匀，背景色 #8B0000。平视正面拍摄，正面柔和打光，无明显阴影，光线均匀。构图为女左男右，女性在前，男性略侧后但贴近，男性肩膀在女性肩膀后侧，外侧肩膀基本齐平，半身照，从胸部上方到头顶，保留适当头顶空间。女性：黑色长发过胸，轻度蓬松，整洁，露出额头、眉毛和双耳，一侧长发在前，优雅端庄；自然露齿微笑，约露 8 颗牙齿，眼神温和亲切，自信幸福；穿纯白色法式轻奢缎面无袖礼服裙，轻裹肩颈，褶皱自然垂落；清透底妆，自然眉形，淡雅眼妆，红色或珊瑚色口红，自然腮红；佩戴简约珍珠吊坠耳环。男性：黑色侧分短发，整齐梳理，干练利落；自然露齿微笑，眼神温和自信，儒雅稳重；穿蓝黑色双排扣西装，内搭纯白标准领衬衫，蓝黑色领带，带金色或浅色小圆点图案，标准领带结；无胡茬。整体效果真实、规范、适合中国结婚登记照审美，照片级写实，高质量证件照质感。注意人物应为成年男女。\"","workdir":"/vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace","yieldMs":120000},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"python3 ~/.openclaw/skills/gpt-image-generator/scripts/generate_image.py --api-url http://china.unicom-online.cloud:8317/v1/responses --api-key sk-K4yKam5TDcrCSs67S --model gpt-image-2 --out-base /vol1/@apphome/trim.openclaw/data/workspace/generated-images/marriage-photo-red-bg-3x2 \\\"结婚登记照，双人半身证件照，两寸比例 3:2，正式、优雅、温馨、庄重而亲切。纯色深红色背景，经典结婚登记照红底，无渐变，色彩饱满均匀，背景色 #8B0000。平视正面拍摄，正面柔和打光，无明显阴影，光线均匀。构图为女左男右，女性在前，男性略侧后但贴近，男性肩膀在女性肩膀后侧，外侧肩膀基本齐平，半身照，从胸部上方到头顶，保留适当头顶空间。女性：黑色长发过胸，轻度蓬松，整洁，露出额头、眉毛和双耳，一侧长发在前，优雅端庄；自然露齿微笑，约露 8 颗牙齿，眼神温和亲切，自信幸福；穿纯白色法式轻奢缎面无袖礼服裙，轻裹肩颈，褶皱自然垂落；清透底妆，自然眉形，淡雅眼妆，红色或珊瑚色口红，自然腮红；佩戴简约珍珠吊坠耳环。男性：黑色侧分短发，整齐梳理，干练利落；自然露齿微笑，眼神温和自信，儒雅稳重；穿蓝黑色双排扣西装，内搭纯白标准领衬衫，蓝黑色领带，